snippet.title: Asking YOU Questions
snippet.description:
I had one of you asking where I sell my vintage designer bags. I just started selling on Poshmark because eBay was giving me some issues. 
I may move it over to my website because Poshmark takes a huge percentage so I have to up my price but if any of you are interested in vintage designer USED bags here is my link

Shop my closet on Poshmark: https://posh.mk/YOjZa9w9Llb. Sign up with my code AMANDARAE380 and get $10.

👇Contact info for charities you can donate to
"Home - Holding Out HELP" https://holdingouthelp.org
https://www.hopeafterpolygamy.org

Also if you are someone trying to leave a polygamous cult you can contact the HOH hotline👇
